d 11 days of celebrations in Brazil, capped off by an unlikely run-in with the former footballer at a rooftop bar.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995721555939, \"rank\": 4.260602253406144e-07, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"11 days\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"celebrations\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"an unlikely run-in\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"the former footballer\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"a rooftop bar\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was having a few drinks and there were a few famous people around, including Ronaldo,\\\" he recalled.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristiano_Ronaldo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0828807995003464e-34, \"text\": \"Ronaldo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristiano_Ronaldo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristiano_Ronaldo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few drinks\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"a few famous people\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had my medal with me and showed him.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my medal\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was like, 'Is that an Olympic gold medal?'\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was about to leave, asked me what I was doing next, and invited me back to his place.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his place\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lift doors were just opening, I did not have time to think, so just said, 'yes' - and next thing I am being driven back to his house by his chauffeur.\\\"\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lift doors\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"next thing\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"his house\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"his chauffeur\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The invitation and acceptance were so quick, he did not have time to let his team-mates with whom he was drinking know about his exit, so texted them the surreal news that he was back at Ronaldo's, playing pool with him and downing drinks.\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristiano_Ronaldo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0828807995003464e-34, \"text\": \"Ronaldo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristiano_Ronaldo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristiano_Ronaldo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The invitation\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"acceptance\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"his team-mates\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"his exit\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"the surreal news\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"pool\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"drinks\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke now has his sights set on gold and another footballing run-in in Paris.\", \"from\": 