stions\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"a 15-month-old son\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"a double shot\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"the traditional slalom\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the new Olympic discipline\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Initially sceptical, he has embraced cross and is ranked world No1.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cross\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"world No1\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The beauty of it is you have got that instant feedback as a spectator of the head to head to who's in first,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The beauty\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"that instant feedback\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectator\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's like a 100m sprint.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 100m sprint\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you watch Usain Bolt run 9.6sec on his own, how boring would that be?\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so impressive when it's eight lanes running together.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight lanes\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love the tactics, the head to head, the mind games, reading other people in certain situations and what's ahead of you.\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tactics\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"the mind games\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"certain situations\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a lot of fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On hand to watch will be his wife and son, who has started shouting \\\"dada\\\" when he appears on TV, parents, in-laws and friends, creating what he calls \\\"a home from home Games\\\".\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"dada\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"laws\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"a home\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"home Games\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This Games has been a long time coming, though.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This Games\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was overlooked for Tokyo, despite being ranked world No1, his lack of selection making him ponder his future.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9763974996103678, \"rank\": 0.024173043927295405, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world No1\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"his future\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were times I was like, 'Where do I go next?\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"',\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to win another Olympic gold but had not made it, and it was such a long wait until the next Games.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another Olympic gold\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"such a long wait\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Games\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a lot of cold, tough days of training ahead and no guarantee then I am going to make the next Games.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"cold, tough days\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3009}, {\"ngram\": \"no guarantee\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Games\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not know if I wanted to put myself through that again.\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt a bit of injustice, but time's a healer and I think it proved a pivotal moment in my career.\\\"\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"injustice\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"a pivotal moment\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3221}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A change of coach to Olympic medallist Campbell Walsh, as well as the prospect of a new event, helped kick-start his return \\\"to the extent I am thinking about the next Games\\\".\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3277, \"end\": 3291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Campbell_Walsh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Campbell Walsh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Campbell_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Campbell_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A change\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"a new event\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"his return\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Games\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clarke thinks it is the tough times that have enabled him to bounce back.\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clarke\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3421}, {\"ngram\": \"the tough times\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost left blind at the age of 15 with an abscess behind his eye, he then contracted secondary meningitis.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"an abscess\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"his eye\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"secondary meningitis\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His consultant told him to take six months out of the water.\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His consultant\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3612}, {\"ngram\": \"six months\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3640}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He returned in three weeks - and has never looked back.\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three weeks\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3776, \"end\": 3785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.866903277270361, \"rank\": 0.15336479860836963, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wik